---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro'
---

<Base title="Terms" description="Terms of use for burleyweststake.com.">
  <header class="page-header">
    <span class="eyebrow">Site Information</span>
    <h1>Terms</h1>
    <p>Terms of use and information about this site.</p>
  </header>

  <article class="prose">
    <p>
      Welcome to the website of the Burley Idaho West Stake of The Church of Jesus Christ of
      Latter-day Saints. This site is maintained by the stake presidency as a way to share
      recordings, presentations, photos, and reflections with our members and friends.
    </p>

    <h2>About this site</h2>
    <p>
      This is an unofficial site operated by the stake presidency of the Burley Idaho West Stake.
      It is not the official site of The Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints. Authoritative
      Church information is available at <a
        href="https://www.churchofjesuschrist.org"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener">churchofjesuschrist.org</a
      > and through Member Tools.
    </p>

    <h2>Content</h2>
    <p>
      Talks, photos, and other materials posted here are shared with the permission of those
      involved. If you are a member of the stake and would like a photo or reference removed,
      please email <a href="mailto:contact@burleyweststake.com">contact@burleyweststake.com</a>.
    </p>

    <h2>Privacy</h2>
    <p>
      We do not collect personal information from site visitors. The site does not use cookies for
      tracking or run third-party analytics.
    </p>

    <h2>Copyright</h2>
    <p>
      Original content on this site is copyright the Burley Idaho West Stake. Quotations from
      scripture, talks, and Church publications belong to their respective copyright holders.
    </p>
  </article>
</Base>
